com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.geom

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.ProxyObject
      • com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.geom.Point

  • public class Point
extends ProxyObject
    The Point object represents a location in a two-dimensional coordinate system, where x represents the horizontal axis and y represents the vertical axis.
